OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff's new returnable
OL,4,Ccoffee cup scheme and how does it work?
OL,6,FA new returnable coffee cup scheme
OL,7,Fwill be launching in the Welsh capital
OL,8,Fnext month to help reduce waste and
OL,9,Ftackle littering across the city.
OL,11,FThe Cardiff Refill Return Cup scheme
OL,12,Fis the first-of-its-kind in Wales and
OL,13,Fenables people to 'borrow' a reusable
OL,14,Ftakeaway cup from a participating cafe
OL,15,Fand return it so that it can be washed
OL,16,Fand used again and again.
OL,18,FIt will roll out across cafes in the
OL,19,Fcity from 4 October.
