OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff's new returnable
OL,4,Ccoffee cup scheme and how does it work?
OL,6,FThe scheme has been delivered by FOR
OL,7,FCardiff with the help of #90,000
OL,8,Ffunding from the UK government through
OL,9,Fthe Shared Prosperity Fund.
OL,11,FFOR Cardiff has partnered with
OL,12,Fenvironmental charity City to Sea
OL,13,Fwhose Refill app will enable people to
OL,14,Ffind locations to pick up and drop off
OL,15,Fa reusable cup.
OL,17,FThe pilot phase of the scheme will run
OL,18,Funtil the end of March 2025 and aims
OL,19,Fto reduce waste and tackle pollution
OL,20,Fand littering across the city.
