OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff's new returnable
OL,4,Ccoffee cup scheme and how does it work?
OL,6,FThe impact of the scheme will be
OL,7,Fmeasured and evaluated by the
OL,8,FGreenwich Business School at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Greenwich and the
OL,10,FCardiff Business School at Cardiff
OL,11,FUniversity, in hopes that the data
OL,12,Fwill help to provide a blueprint for
OL,13,Ffuture schemes across the UK.
OL,15,FAn estimated 2.5 billion takeaway
OL,16,Fcoffee cups are used and thrown away
OL,17,Feach year in the UK - enough to
OL,18,Fstretch around the world five and a
OL,19,Fhalf times if placed end to end - and
OL,20,F99% of these are currently not
OL,21,Frecycled.
