OL,3,CWhat is Cardiff's new returnable
OL,4,Ccoffee cup scheme and how does it work?
OL,6,FThe UK uses 10,000 coffee cups every
OL,7,Ftwo minutes.
OL,9,FCardiff cafes and coffee shops who
OL,10,Fhave so far signed up to be part of
OL,11,Fthe scheme include Waterloo Tea in
OL,12,FWyndham Arcade, Pettigrew Bakeries, Da
OL,13,FCoffee and, Bird & Blend Tea.
OL,15,FEach venue has committed to offering a
OL,16,Fminimum of 15p discount on the price
OL,17,Fof a coffee for anyone using the
OL,18,FCardiff Refill Return Cup scheme.
